I apologize for the confusion. The error is due to the backslashes and line breaks causing issues. Let me provide you with a corrected command that you can directly copy and paste:

```bash
gcloud organizations add-iam-policy-binding 135174585026 --member=user:jesse@taey.ai --role=roles/cloudbuild.builds.builder
```

This command should work correctly when copied and pasted into your terminal.
